      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl">
        Beyond receptors and storage diseases: understanding gangliosides as a fundamental 
        <strong>communication infrastructure</strong> that enables neurons to send, receive, 
        and selectively filter signals across time and distance.
      </p>
